\c 1
\s Mozisi anorondedzera zvakaitika pakufamba kweVaIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Awa mashoko Mozisi aakataura kuna Israeri wose mhiri kwaJoridhani murenje, mubani pakatarisana neSufi, pakati peParani neTofera neRabhani\x + 1 Zvak. 25.1. Num. 10.12.\x* neHazeroti neDhizahabhi\x + Num. 11.35. 12.16. 33.17.\x*.
\v 2 \add Pane\add* mazuva gumi nerimwe kubva paHorebhu, \add ne\add*nzira yegomo reSeiri kusvika paKadheshi-Bharineya\x + Num. 13.26. 32.8. 34.4. 2.14. 9.23.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino zvakaitika mugore remakumi mana, mumwedzi wegumi neumwe, nerekutanga remwedzi\x + Num. 33.38.\x*, Mozisi wakataura kuvana vaIsraeri zvichienderana nezvose Jehovha zvaaiva amupa kuva murairo kwavari;
\v 4 shure kwekunge arova Sihoni mambo weVaAmori\x + Num. 21.24,26.\x* waiva agere muHeshibhoni\x + Num. 21.24,26.\x*, naOgi mambo weBhashani\x + Num. 21.33. Josh. 12.4. 13.12. 3.1,10.\x* waiva agere paAshitaroti paEdhirei.
\v 5 Nechekuno kwaJoridhani munyika yeMoabhu Mozisi wakatanga kududzira murairo uyu achiti:
\v 6 Jehovha Mwari wedu wakataura kwatiri muHorebhu achiti: Magara nguva yakakwana mugomo iri\x + Eki. 19.1. Num. 10.11; 2.3.\x*.
\v 7 Dzokai imwi mubve muende kugomo reVaAmori nekwese kwakavakidzana navo, mubani, muzvikomo, nemumupata, nekuchamhembe, nekumahombekombe egungwa, nyika yeVaKenani, neRebhanoni, kusvika kurwizi rukuru, rwizi Furati.
\v 8 Onai, ndaisa nyika pamberi penyu; pindai, mudye nhaka yenyika Jehovha yaakapikira madzibaba enyu, Abhurahama, Isaka, naJakove, kuvapa \add iyo\add* nekumbeu yavo shure kwavo\x + Gen. 12.7. 15.18. 17.7,8. 26.4. 28.13. 50.24.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Uye ndataura kwamuri nguva ino ndichiti: Handigoni kukutakurai ndiri ndega\x + Num. 11.14. Eki. 18.18\x*.
\v 10 Jehovha Mwari wenyu wakakuwanzai\x + Gen. 15.5. Det. 28.62.\x*; zvino tarirai, nhasi mava senyeredzi dzekumatenga pakuwanda.
\v 11 Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba enyu ngaawedzere kwamuri, sezvamakaita, kakapetwa kane churu, akuropafadzei, sezvaakataura kwamuri\x + 2 Zvak. 24.3.\x*.
\v 12 Ndiri ndoga ndingatakura sei\x + 1 Madz. 3.8,9.\x* urema hwenyu nemutoro wenyu negakava renyu\x + Isa. 1.14.\x*?
\v 13 Zvipei varume vakachenjera, uye vanonzwisisa, uye vanozikanwa kumarudzi enyu, ndivaise vave misoro yenyu\x + Eki. 18.21. Num. 11.16,17.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino makandipindura mukati: Shoko ramataura rakanaka kuriita.
\v 15 Zvino ndakatora misoro yemarudzi enyu, varume vakachenjera uye vanozikanwa, ndikavaisa vakava misoro pamusoro penyu, vakuru vezvuru, nevakuru vemazana, nevakuru vemakumi mashanu, nevakuru vemakumi\x + Eki. 18.25.\x*, nevabati vemarudzi enyu\x + Num. 11.16.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino ndakaraira vatongi venyu nenguva iyo ndichiti: Inzwai z\add viri\add* pakati pehama dzenyu, mutonge zvakarurama pakati pemunhu nehama yake, nemutorwa wake\x + Joh. 7.24.\x*.
\v 17 Musatarira zviso pakutonga; inzwai mudiki semukuru; musatya chiso chemunhu\x + Rev. 19.15.16.19. 1 Zvak. 16.7. Zvir. 24.23. Jak. 2.1,9.\x*; nokuti kutonga ndekwaMwari; uye nyaya inorema kwamuri muchaiuisa kwandiri\x + 2 Makor. 19.6.\x*, zvino ndichainzwa\x + Eki. 18.22,26.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino nenguva iyo ndakakurairai zvinhu zvose zvamunofanira kuita.
\p
\v 19 Zvino takabva paHorebhu, takafamba murenje iro rose guru rinotyisa, ramakaona nenzira yegomo reVaAmori, sezvakatiraira Jehovha Mwari wedu\x + 8.15. Num. 10.12. Jer. 2.6.\x*; ndokusvika paKadheshi-Bharineya\x + 1.2. 2.14.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino ndakati kwamuri: Masvika pagomo reVaAmori, Jehovha Mwari wedu raachapa kwatiri.
\v 21 Tarirai, Jehovha Mwari wenyu wakaisa nyika iyo pamberi penyu; kwirai mugare nhaka \add yayo\add*, sezvakataura Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba enyu kwamuri; musatya kana kuvhunduka\x + Josh. 1.9. Det. 31.8.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino makaswedera kwandiri mese mukati: Ngatitume varume mberi kwedu kuti vatishorere nyika, vagodzosa shoko kwatiri, nzira yatichakwira nayo, nemaguta atichapinda kwaari.
\v 23 Zvino shoko rakava rakanaka pameso angu; naizvozvo ndakatora kwamuri varume gumi nevaviri, murume umwe parudzi\x + Num. 13.3.\x*.
\v 24 Ivo ndokutendeuka, ndokukwira mugomo\x + Num. 13.22-27.\x* vasvika mumupata weEshikori, ndokuishora.
\v 25 Zvino vakatora zvemuchero wenyika mumaoko avo, ndokuzviburusira kwatiri, ndokutidzosera shoko, ndokuti: Inyika yakanaka Jehovha Mwari wedu yaanotipa.
\v 26 Zvakadaro hamuna kuda kukwira, asi makamukira muromo waJehovha Mwari wenyu\x + 1.43. Josh. 1.18. Map. 107.11.\x*.
\v 27 Zvino makanyunyuta mumatende enyu, ndokuti\x + Map. 106.25. Num. 14.1-4.\x*: Nokuti Jehovha wakativenga, wakatibudisa munyika yeEgipita, kutiisa muruoko rweVaAmori kutiparadza\x + 9.28.\x*.
\v 28 Tichakwirepi? Hama dzedu dzanyautsa moyo wedu\x + Josh. 14.8.\x* dzichiti: Vanhu vakuru uye varefu kutipfuura; maguta makuru uye akashoshewa kusvika kumatenga\x + Num. 13.28-33. Det. 9.1,2.\x*; uyewo vana vaAnaki\x + Num. 13.22.\x* ta\add va\add*onako.
\v 29 Zvino ndakati kwamuri: Musavhunduka, kana kuvatya.
\v 30 Jehovha Mwari wenyu anokutungamirirai, ndiye achakurwirai, sezvaakakuitirai zvose paEgipita pamberi pemeso enyu\x + Eki. 14.14,25. Neh. 4.20.\x*,
\v 31 nemurenje pamakaona kuti Jehovha Mwari wenyu wakakutakura semurume anotakura mwanakomana wake, panzira yose yamakafamba, kusvika masvika panzvimbo ino\x + Eki. 19.4. 32.11,12. Isa. 46.3,4. 63.9. Hos. 11.3. Mab. 13.18.\x*.
\v 32 Asi pachinhu ichi hamuna kutenda muna Jehovha Mwari wenyu\x + Map. 106.24. Jud. 5.\x*;
\v 33 iye wakakutungamirirai panzira\x + Eki. 13.21.\x* kukutsvakirai nzvimbo kuti mudzike matende, mumoto usiku, kukutaridzai nzira yamuchafamba, uye mugore masikati\x + Num. 10.33.\x*.
\v 34 Zvino Jehovha wakanzwa inzwi remashoko enyu, ndokutsamwa, ndokupika achiti\x + 2.14,15.\x*:
\v 35 Zvirokwazvo haako kuvarume ava, zera iri rakaipa, achaona nyika yakanaka, yandakapikira kupa madzibaba enyu\x + Num. 14.22,23,29. Map. 95.11.\x*,
\v 36 kunze kwaKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune, iye achaiona; uye ndichapa kwaari nekuvana vake nyika yaakatsika, nokuti wakatevera Jehovha zvakazara\x + Num. 14.24,30. Josh. 14.9.\x*.
\v 37 Neni Jehovha wakanditsamwira nekuda kwenyu achiti: Iwewo haungapindi ikoko\x + 4.21. Num. 20.12. 27.13,14.3.26. 32.51. 34.4. Map. 106.32.\x*.
\v 38 Joshua mwanakomana waNuni\x + Num. 13.16.\x* anomira pamberi pako, iye achapinda ikoko\x + Eki. 24.13. 1 Zvak. 16.22.\x*; umusimbise, nokuti iye achaita Israeri adye nhaka yavo\x + Num. 27.18-20. Det. 31.7,23.\x*.
\v 39 Nevanana venyu vamakati vachajimbiwa, nevana venyu\x + Num. 14.3,31.\x* vasingazivi nhasi zvakanaka nezvakaipa, ivo vachapinda ikoko, uye ndichaipa kwavari, uye ivo vachaigara nhaka\x + Isa. 7.15,16.\x*.
\v 40 Asi imwi zvitendeukirei mugofamba makananga kurenje, nzira yeGungwa Dzvuku\x + Num. 14.25; Det. 2.1.\x*.
\v 41 Zvino makapindura ndokuti kwandiri: Takatadzira Jehovha, isu tichakwira tigonorwa zvichienderana nezvose Jehovha Mwari wedu zvaakatiraira\x + Num. 14.40.\x*. Zvino makati mashonga umwe neumwe zvombo zvake zvehondo, makafunga kuti zvakareruka kukwira mugomo.
\v 42 Zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Iti kwavari: Musakwira kana kurwa, nokuti handisi pakati penyu; zvimwe mungarohwa pamberi pevavengi venyu\x + Num. 14.42.\x*.
\v 43 Zvino ndakataura kwamuri, asi hamuna kuteerera, ndokumukira murairo waJehovha\x + 1.26.\x*, mukaita manyawi, ndokukwira mugomo.
\v 44 Zvino VaAmori vaigara mugomo iro vakabuda kumirisana nemwi, ndokukudzingirirai\x + Num. 14.45.\x* sezvinoita nyuchi, ndokukuparadzai paSeiri kusvika paHorima\x + Map. 118.12.\x*.
\v 45 Zvino makadzoka ndokuchema pamberi paJehovha, asi Jehovha haana kuteerera inzwi renyu, kana kurerekera nzeve dzake kwamuri.
\v 46 Zvino makagara paKadheshi mazuva mazhinji, semazuva amakagara\add po\add*\x + Num. 20.1,22. Vato. 11.17.\x*.